#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/08b_The_Tides_of_War.cfg:441
msgid ""
"Look there! The undead have broken through Sir Gerrick’s line! Alas, he is "
"lost!"
